<function>

access:   public

name: from

param: string|object, $spec

param: array|string, $cols, NULL

return: Solar_Sql_Select

</function>

Adds a FROM table and columns to the query.

* Parameters:

 * string|object //$spec//: If a Solar_Sql_Table object, the table to select from; if a string, the table name to select from.

 * array|string //$cols//: The columns to select from this table.

* Returns Solar_Sql_Select

Adds a FROM table and columns to the query.